graph TB
    subgraph "User Interface"
        Dashboard[HTML Dashboard<br/>ArchiMate View]
    end

    subgraph "Orchestration Layer"
        Orchestrator[MCP Client<br/>Orchestrator<br/>Flask REST API]
    end

    subgraph "Service Layer - Docker Containers"
        CS[Customer Service<br/>MCP Server<br/>JSON-RPC]
        OS[Order Service<br/>MCP Server<br/>JSON-RPC]
    end

    subgraph "Data Layer"
        RDF1[(RDF Graph<br/>Customer Data<br/>in-memory)]
        RDF2[(RDF Graph<br/>Order Data<br/>in-memory)]
    end

    subgraph "Shared Ontology"
        Ontology[ecommerce.ttl<br/>RDF Schema<br/>Turtle Format]
    end

    Dashboard -->|HTTP/REST| Orchestrator
    Orchestrator -->|Docker API| CS
    Orchestrator -->|Docker API| OS
    Orchestrator -->|MCP/JSON-RPC| CS
    Orchestrator -->|MCP/JSON-RPC| OS
    CS --> RDF1
    OS --> RDF2
    RDF1 -.->|follows| Ontology
    RDF2 -.->|follows| Ontology

